18:12.766 --> 18:13.206
Koenig.

18:13.767 --> 18:17.652
It's K-O-E-N-I-G.

18:17.813 --> 18:18.474
And his first name?

18:19.075 --> 18:19.495
Eberhard.

18:19.856 --> 18:20.997
Eberhard Koenig.

18:21.017 --> 18:25.043
