Decretum.

19:24.430 --> 19:25.091
Decretum.

19:25.411 --> 19:28.377
D-E-C-R-E-T-U-M.

19:28.657 --> 19:31.643
D-E-C-R-E-T-U-M.

19:31.883 --> 19:32.544
The Decretum.

19:32.664 --> 19:33.806
That's what you call this book.

19:34.027 --> 19:35.409
Yeah, this is the book.

19:35.510 --> 19:36.571
And this was printed where?

19:37.173 --> 19:37.653
In Mainz.

19:38.054 --> 19:39.116
In Mainz.

19:39.136 --> 19:40.238
1472.

19:41.467 --> 19:46.336
And you said Schaeffer was the printer, right?

19:46.357 --> 19:46.878
Schaeffer, yeah.

19:46.898 --> 19:48.380
Peter Schaeffer was the printer.

19:48.601 --> 19:51.967
Look, you see here, it's very famous.

19:52.969 --> 19:54.773
Printing marks.

19:54.853 --> 20:00.243
And you see here, Petrus Schaeffer, the longtime Continental Cutis.

20:00.264 --> 20:03.610
